Daisy Goodwin has had problems with head lice since she was 19 . 
  She says she has suffered with the parasites almost 100 times since then . 
  She was never affected as a child but says she got them for the first time at 19 . 
  Daisy says she was lucky to have a few years free of them . 
  But she says the parasites returned when she had children . 
  She said you can win the battle but it is not easy . 
 